RelatedSentence: CEDAR FALLS -- The Cedar Prairie Group of the Sierra Club will host the weekly walk at Eldora 's Wildcat Trail , 31510 215th St. , on Thursday .
Participants may meet at the Cedar Falls Visitors and Tourism Center parking lot , 6510 Hudson Road , at 9 a.m. to caravan and carpool to the park or meet at the park at approximately 9:45 .
